definition: conclusion/verdict/CL:個|个[ge4]/to conclude/to reach a verdict
knot/sturdy/bond/to tie/to bind/to check out (of a hotel)

sentences.english: Conclusion Complex treatment is the most effective method for treatment of residual brun wound.
sentences.chinese: 结论综合治疗是治疗烧伤残余创面的重要方法。

sentences.english: That's according to a new AP Ipsos poll.

sentences.english: Conclusions Uterine cavity and fallopian tube abnormalities were the important reason of female infertile.

sentences.english: Conclusion Mutations in the CYP1B1 gene have genetic heterogeneity.

sentences.english: Conclusions Osteoclast-mediated bone resorption was inhibited by the bisphosphonate administration.

sentences.english: The results provide empirical foundation for model-building and simulations.
